{"tid":323043,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥斯達:後悔當年參與內訌做掉了摩連奴","createTime":"2017-07-15T10:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T16:35:14.000Z","uid":49079,"like":62,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd61efe6ba8569cd5c4ce5016d3cb053424529f3","tid":323043,"uid":49079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T10:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://n2.hk/u/attachments/day_170715/20170715_38fc5c0f23a72deb4651TDphl5VG2pXf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fu%2Fattachments%2Fday_170715%2F20170715_38fc5c0f23a72deb4651TDphl5VG2pXf.jpg&h=cd0be136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太陽報近日披露，車路士前鋒哥斯達說出來當年車路士隊更衣室裡的一些事情。<br />\n哥斯達說道：&ldquo;我當時被一些人影響了，他們私下里對主教練與隊醫的事不滿。我當時很生氣，認為他簡直就是一個壞蛋；如今我才知道他是一個多麼大度的人，壞人留在了這裡。&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;我知道他無法原諒我當年對他所做的一切，在我危難時他總是保護我，可是在他最困難的時候我卻丟給他一件訓練服。&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;我離開是因為我發現自己做錯了，他們發現我不能對這件事有清楚的認識。跟我有一樣想法的人也踢不上球，只能選擇離開。&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;願他一切都好。&rdquo;如今事件的主角都離開了故事的舞台，策劃事件的人擁有了那個舞台。在足球世界裡，這樣的事情必須要面對。"},{"pid":"444b12173afd31d0bc4458206682390a971d0044","tid":323043,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T10:09:38.000Z","msg":"呢條友難聽d講  搞風搞小 正小人"},{"pid":"614059b3e90020aa41b742ba328f441c428b8650","tid":323043,"uid":100393,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T10:10:24.000Z","msg":"暗示hazard帶頭？"},{"pid":"2559558012bac651f078cea79c93978928596a95","tid":323043,"uid":1289,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T10:16:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c3bb4298d0bbefd42422e328777f3dc63c06b01","tid":323043,"uid":12736,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T10:18:19.000Z","msg":"太陽報報依啲野好準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係轉會多吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid